Swipe to review the highlights from our GE Girls Camps across the globe! 🌍

This summer, we brought together middle school girls from across the globe for immersive, hands-on STEM activities as part of our mission to empower the next generation of innovators. 

With the guidance and support of our engineers and passionate GE HealthCare volunteers, we sparked a love for science technology, engineering, and mathematics in these future leads. 

Let’s continue to inspire the next generation of STEM leaders! 👩‍🔬
